snippet.title: Spin Rhythm XD - Early Access Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Spin Rhythm XD, the action-packed intergalactic rhythm game with the juiciest beats in the universe. Developed by Super Spin Digital. 

Coming to Steam October 22, 2019 (Early Access) and Switch (TBA) 2020.

RRP $USD19.99 (EA)

https://spinrhythmgame.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SpinRhythmGame/
Discord: https://discord.gg/P9AP4bR
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1058830/Spin_Rhythm_XD/

Prepare to enter the rhythm dimension.
